  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sport Village</strong> 148 elegantly appointed twin rooms with bath, shower, hairdryer, satellite TV and safe.</p>
<p><strong>Standard rooms (23sqm approx) </strong>have twin or double beds, bath with shower attachment, satellite TV, minibar and safe deposit box.</p>
<p><strong>Duplex rooms (32sqm approx) </strong>are larger with mountain views</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites (50sqm approx) </strong>are ideal for families and have a lounge with sofa bed and a twin or double bedroom.</p>
<p><strong>‘Relax’ Junior Suites (56sqm approx)</strong> have a massage bath in the bathroom, lounge with one sofa bed and a twin or double bedroom.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
